(7046, 'benazepril hydrochloride', 'N/A', 'minor', 'The pharmacokinetics of benazepril are not affected by the following drugs: hydrochlorothiazide, furosemide, chlorthalidone, digoxin, propranolol, atenolol, nifedipine, amlodipine, naproxen, acetylsalicylic acid, or cimetidine.', 'DailyMed'),
