(29393, 'ciprofloxacin hydrochloride   tablet', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (but not acetyl salicylic acid) in combination of very high doses of quinolones have been shown to provoke convulsions in pre-clinical studies.', 'DailyMed'),
